text: Holger Schön (30 March 1910 - 25 March 1980) was a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1932 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1980 deaths Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Swedish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
